                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2>How to pay your Postpaid Bill or TopUp your prepaid number.</h2>
                <p>To pay your bill takes the following steps:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        After entering your ATM PIN number, select the Utility Bill Payment option on the ATM screen
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Select ‘Warid Telecom’ from the list that appears on the screen
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Enter your mobile number for which you want TopUp or Bill payment
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Select your account
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Select the Amount for Top up or enter the Bill Payment amount for post pay
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Acknowledge the entered information
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Collect / Save the receipt.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>For more information kindly contact your bank or visit <a href="http://www.1link.net.pk/" target="_blank">www.1link.net.pk</a></p>
                <h2>Charges</h2>
                <p>This service is free of cost and has no hidden charges.</p>
